snippet.title: Johnny Depp Can't Stop Laughing At Amber Heard Attorney
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Can't Stop Laughing At Amber Heard Attorney.

During the cross-examination of Starling Jenkins, the defense questioned him about an incident between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. The defense asked Starling if Depp was trying to take care of his business inside the house and if his "thing" was out of his pants.
